records.addlTxt:
Zoom appearances.
Defendant in custody at Manitowoc County Jail.
GUILTY plea entered to count 1, felony bail jumping. Convicted.
The State moves to dismiss and read in counts 2, 3 and 4.  Motion granted.
Sentence Withheld.  Defendant is placed on probation to DOC for two (2) years.
Conditions of probation:
1)	Assessment, treatment, counseling as deemed appropriate by the Department's assessment process;
2)	Have no contact with anyone under the age of 18 unless approved by the agent;
3)	Spend sixty (60) days in the county jail, under the Huber Law, stayed and to be imposed at the agent's discretion and upon order of the court;
4)	Pay court costs;
5)	pay supervision fees in an amount to be determined by DOC;
6)	provide DNA sample;
7)	any and all treatment as recommended by the agent;
8)	maintain fulltime employment, schooling, treatment at the agent's discretion.
The defendant has credit for 40 days, if revoked.
Minutes.
